mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "'Square Dancing' by Lee Helsel Reprint from Nov. 1957", "'A Viewpoint Changes' By Dean A. Krenz", "The Walkthru", "Interview: Bruce Johnson", "Report from the Round Dance Standardization Panel-Part 1", "Style Series", "Caller Roundup", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Jamboree in Japan", "Workshop", "National Convention", "Paging the Roundancers: Don and Pete Hickman", "Caller of the Month: Howie Shirley", "Current Best Sellers", and "Experimental Lab".
